aanaMdee naH puneeyaadarinalinagadaa shaMkhapaaNirmukuMdaH || 1 || 

bhUH paadau yasya naabhirviyadasuranilashchaMdra sUryau cha nEtrE
karNaavaashaaH shirO dyaurmukhamapi dahanO yasya vaastEyamabdhiH |
aMtaHsthaM yasya vishvaM suranarakhagagObhOgigaMdharvadaityaiH
chitraM raMramyatE taM tribhuvana vapuShaM viShNumeeshaM namaami || 2 || 

Om shaaMtaakaaraM bhujagashayanaM padmanaabhaM surEshaM
vishvaadhaaraM gaganasadRushaM mEghavarNaM shubhaaMgam |
lakShmeekaaMtaM kamalanayanaM yOgibhirdhyaanagamyaM
vaMdE viShNuM bhavabhayaharaM sarvalOkaikanaatham || 3 || 

mEghashyaamaM peetakaushEyavaasaM 
shreevatsaaMkaM kaustubhOdbhaasitaaMgam |
puNyOpEtaM puMDareekaayataakShaM 
viShNuM vaMdE sarvalOkaikanaatham || 4 || 

namaH samastabhUtaanaamaadibhUtaaya bhUbhRutE |
anEkarUparUpaaya viShNavE prabhaviShNavE || 5 || 

sashaMkhachakraM sakireeTakuMDalaM
sapeetavastraM saraseeruhEkShaNam |
sahaaravakShaHsthalakaustubhashriyaM
namaami viShNuM shirasaa chaturbhujam || 6 || 

ChaayaayaaM paarijaatasya hEmasiMhaasanOpari
aaseenamaMbudashyaamamaayataakShamalaMkRutam |
